"The WPA/WPA2 PSK passphrase was either too long (more than 64 characters) or "
"too short (less than 8 characters)."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r cyfrinair WPA/WPA2 PSK naill yn rhy hir (mwy na 64 nod) neu yn rhy fyr "
"(llai na 8 nod)."

#. Type: string
